263237.「ただいまより 第９回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発表:
We will now announce the results of the 9th
Astoltia Queen Contest!

263238.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who will be the queen of the Chocolat Fontenay
Castle? The result will finally be revealed!

263239.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！:
Ladies and gentlemen! Please pay attention to
the stage!

264118.「ただいまより 第９回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加する:
We are pleased to introduce you to the
beautiful women who will be participating in
the 9th Astoltia Queen Contest!

264119.「前大会で 好成績をおさめ\n 見事 出場権を獲得した ４名に加え……:
In addition to the four who qualified for the
previous tournament with excellent results

264120.「ファルパパ神による特別推薦枠 ２名と\n 総勢４８人の予選を勝ち抜いた 上位２:
The top two winners of the 48-people preliminary contest, plus the two specially recommended by Falpapa God, will compete for
the top eight beauties!

264121.「まずは 前大会の覇者が 堂々の登場だ！\n 覇道を突き進む バルディスタの魔王:
First of all, the champion of the previous tournament made a grand entrance! Valdista's Demon King, who has been on a high road,
grabbed the crown in his first appearance in this year's tournament!

264122.「またしても 我々は 氷の微笑の\n トリコにされてしまうのか！？\n 死を運ぶ:
Once again, we are being turned into a
tricolour of icy smiles! The ice witch who
carries death! Valeria!

264123.「フフ……つくづく 甘い連中だな。\n 一度 明け渡した玉座を 取り戻せると\n:
You really are a very naive bunch, aren't you?
Do you really think you can get back the
throne you once surrendered?

264124.「やる前から 結果は見えているが……\n まあ いい。余興に つきあってやろう。:
The result is obvious even before we start,
but that's okay. I'll go along with the
entertainment.

264125.「この私が 女王であることに\n 異を唱える者は いるか？ ならば 前に出よ。\:
Does anyone dispute that I am the queen? Then
step forward. I will punish you myself.

264126.「いい気になるな 氷の魔女！！\n 私が 玉座から引きずりおろしてやるッ！:
Don't get carried away, Ice Witch! I will drag
you down from the throne!

264127.「おおっと！ いつか見た光景が ふたたび！\n 前大会の 雪辱なるかーっ！？:
Oh, wow! Once again, we see the same scene we
saw one day! Will we make up for our defeat in
the last tournament?

264128.「ひとりの聖騎士から 受け継いだ \n 博愛の心が 悪をこらしめる 原動力。:
The philanthropic spirit he inherited from a
knight is the driving force behind his crusade
against evil.

264129.「いつか あの人のような パラディンに……。\n その思いを胸に 今日も今日とて:
Someday, I will be a paladin like him. With that thought in my heart, I'm going to defeat evil today and tomorrow! But do you also want
a little money?

264131.「我が名は 黄金のパラディン！\n 今度こそ クイーンの座を 手にしてみせる！:
My name is Golden Paladin, and this time I
will be crowned queen!

264132.「あんじょう 見たってや……っと！？ コホン！: Anjo, you finally saw it! COUGH!

264133.「見てるがいいッ！\n 我ら パラディンの示す 博愛の精神が\n バレンタインの:
Watch and see! The spirit of philanthropy that
we at paladin have shown will protect the
future of Valentine's Day!

264134.「記憶喪失の少女が 背負わされていた運命は\n あまりにも 過酷だった！:
The fate of the girl with amnesia was too
cruel!

264135.「それでも 彼女は １枚でも多くのスケッチを\n 描き続ける。みずからが 愛した:
Even so, she continues to draw as many
sketches as possible. As if to imprint the
world she loved deeply in her heart.

264136.「魔界にも 厚い支持層を持つ 聖女は\n 今度こそ クイーンの座を 射止めること:
Will the saintly maiden with a thick support
base in Demon World be able to win the queen's
title this time? Maiden of miasma Illusia!

264137.「私が クイーンの座につくことで\n しあわせになれる人が いるのなら\n 私…:
If there is someone who will be happy with my
being queen, I will try my best!

264138.「ねえ 少しだけ 私にチカラを貸して。\n あなたとなら どこまでも 行ける気が:
Hey, lend me your strength for a moment. I
feel like I can go anywhere with you.

264139.「続いては この方！\n どんな そしりを受けようと 己の愛を\n つらぬくこと:
Next is this one! I will not hesitate to stand
by my love, no matter what the consequences!

264140.「折れることを知らない 鋼の意志で\n 今度こそ 栄冠を つかみ取れっ！\n 歴:
With a will of unbreakable steel, grab the
crown this time! ally Kamil was erased from
history!

264141.「これは 奇跡でしょうか？\n 私に もう一度 機会が与えられるとは……。:
Is this a miracle? That I would be given
another chance.

264142.「見ていてください アルヴァン。\n 全身全霊を賭して戦う 勇姿を！: Watch, Alvan, as he fights with all his might!

264143.「かならずや 栄冠を つかみ取り\n これまで 私を応援してくれた すべての人々:
I pledge that I will win the crown and repay
all the people who have supported me!

264144.「続いて ファルパパ神による 特別推薦枠２名！\n まずは 魔界からお越しの こ:
Next, we have two special nominees by Falpapa
God! First, we have this gentleman from Demon
World!

264145.「ツンと すました横顔を ふり向かせたい！\n その時点で 彼女の術中に はまっ:
I want her to turn her head to look at me! At that point, you've fallen for her tricks! Linberry is a very prestigious and selfish
young lady!

264146.「どの参加者も なかなかの美形ぞろいね。\n みーんな ベラストル家の 使用人と:
All the participants are quite beautiful. You
should all be hired as servants at Belastre
house.

264147.「だ・け・ど 賢明な 紳士淑女の皆様は \n この中で 誰が クイーンにふさわし:
But you wise ladies and gentlemen can already
see who among you is fit to be queen, can't
you?

264148.「いいかしら？ 私以外に 投票したら\n 全員 火あぶりにするわよ！:
May I? If you vote for anyone but me, I'll
burn you all at the stake!

264149.「次の推薦枠は このお方。 \n 趣味は 食っちゃ寝。ヒマつぶしのために\n 今:
The next nomination is this gentleman.His
hobby is to eat and sleep. He is a wandering
swordsman who runs east and west to kill time.

264151.「ファビエルのやつから クイーンになって\n 名を上げれば 何かと 生きていくの:
I've heard from the Fabiel guy that if you
become a queen and make a name for yourself,
it will make life a lot easier.

264152.「ううっ 勝てる気がしない。: Ugh, I don't think I can win.

264153.「だが 伏して 頼もう！\n こんな無気力な私を 憎からず思うなら\n どうか:
But I'm going to get down and ask you! If you
hate me for being such an apathetic person,
please give me your votes!

264154.「さあ ここからは 激しい予選を勝ち抜いた \n 猛者たちを ご紹介しましょう。:
Now, let us introduce you to the fierce
competitors who made it through the intense
qualifying rounds.

264155.「こんな女性が 指導者だったら\n 誰もが よろこんで ひざまずくだろう！\n:
If such a woman were a leader, everyone would
be delighted to kneel in her presence!
Seraphi, the blue guide of Al-Ahagiro!

264156.「えへへ。たくさんの人の 応援があったから\n またまた コンテストに出られたよ:
Hehehe. Thanks to the support of so many people, I was able to participate in the contest again. I'll do my best to win the
first prize.

264159.「うんうん。疲れが とれたみたいね。\n それじゃ 今年のバレンタインも\n み:
Yeah, yeah, yeah. I guess I'm getting over my
fatigue. Well then, let's all have a great
Valentine's Day together this year! Oh!

264160.「最後に紹介するのは もちろん あの人だ！\n クイーンの座に 返り咲くべく\n:
Last but not least, of course, is that man! A brave warrior who has fought in the past to win back the queen's title, he has come
through the qualifying rounds!

264161.「きびしい修行で得たのは 強さだけじゃない。\n 見よッ！ 内面から にじみ出る:
Strength is not the only thing I gained through hard training. Behold! The beauty that oozes from within! The battlePurineSeth Hero
Princess Anlucia of purity!

264162.「みなさんの 応援のおかげで\n ふたたび クイーンの座を手にする\n チャンス:
Thanks to your support, I have the chance to
be queen again.

264163.「修行を経て 生まれ変わった私を\n しかと 目に焼きつけてください。\n 勇者:
I hope you will witness the rebirth of me
through my training. I will show you a battle
that lives up to the name of Hero!

264164.「……以上 ８名の美女たちが\n クイーンの座をかけて コンテストを争います。:
These eight beauties will compete for the
title of queen.

264165.「栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 果たして 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will be crowned with glory? It is you who
will decide!

264166.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n 今回も選りすぐりの美女が そろいました。\n:
What do you think ? We have a great selection of beauties for you to choose from this time. Did you find your favorite
one?

264167.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n あなたの持つ票を 投じてあげ:
If you decide on a beauty you think deserves
to be queen, cast your vote for her.

264168.「なお 投票につきましては 集計係モカの所で\n おこなっていただくことに なっ:
Voting is to be done at Tallier Mocha's
office.

264169.「票を投じましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
After you cast your vote, please stop by my
place for a chat. I'll be outside.
